Lean is an interactive theorem prover based on dependent type theory.
It features a high level of automation compared to competing systems
such as Coq and Agda.

Lean's documentation lives online:

* Theorem Proving in Lean:
  https://leanprover.github.io/theorem_proving_in_lean/
* The Lean Reference Manual:
  https://leanprover.github.io/reference/

If you are using Emacs, you will want to install the lean Emacs mode,
via M-x package-install RET lean-mode RET.
